                                          throws UnknownHostException,
                                                 NumberFormatException
        Utility method to extract the ip address and port number from the input String.

        Parameters:
        input - A textual representation of the IP address and optional port number.
        Returns:
        a HashMap containing the converted InetAddress representation of the IP and an integer representation of the port number
        Throws:
        UnknownHostException - on processing error.
        NumberFormatException
